    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with the highest level of care. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner.",
